<author>ạlạ̉b fạdy jndḥ, sẖạrl sẖlạlạ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lw knt tdryn yạ nfsy mn hw yswʿ
 ạ̹smh mn ạ̹tẖmk ysẖfy
 ysẖfyk yswʿ
 hw yḥbk ạ̉nt lh lạ tnksry
 hw yḥmyk kwny lh lạ tyạ̉sy
 hw sẖạfyk hlly lh lạtrkʿy
 hw yrwyk sbḥy lh sbḥy lh
 kl sẖỷ mnh nʿmh lạ tnsy ạ̹smh yswʿ
 2- lw knt tdryn yạ nfsy km bḥbk yswʿ
 ḥbh mn kẖwfk ysẖfy
 ysẖfyk yswʿ
 hw yjdẖbk rnmy lh ln tʿṭsẖy
 hw ygẖmrk ạ̉ʿzfy lh lạ trkʿy
 hw yrfʿk ạ̉rqṣ lh lạ tyạ̉sy
 hw yḥfẓk ạ̉htfy lh ạ̹htfy lh
 kl sẖỷ mnh nʿmh lạ tnsy ạ̹smh yswʿ</lyrics>
<title>lw knti tdryn yạ nfsy</title>
</song>